                              'Lightit' 2.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Lightit' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where the goal is to switch on
all the lightbulbs on an hexagonally shaped board. When you
complete a game board, Lightit displays a new board, where more
lightbulbs are turned on or off...

  The game offers two difficulty levels: @{" Easy " link play} or @{" Harder " link play}.

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

